Add Phase 2 & 3: all collectors, intelligence pipeline, full dashboard

Phase 2:
- Reddit, Stocks (Yahoo Finance), Weather (wttr.in), GitHub collectors
- React dashboard with draggable/resizable widgets (react-grid-layout)
- Stock Ticker, Weather, AI Digest, and Trending widgets
- WebSocket server for live updates
- Dark theme with responsive design

Phase 3:
- Two-stage LLM intelligence pipeline
- Ollama integration for local relevance scoring
- Claude/OpenAI integration for deep analysis
- Summarization, auto-tagging, and interest matching
- Budget-aware with daily call limits
- Graceful degradation (works without any LLM)

Infrastructure:
- GitHub Actions CI (lint, build, type-check)
- GitHub Actions release (cross-compile for linux/mac amd64/arm64)
- Docker + docker-compose setup
- Single binary deployment via rust-embed

